tps://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国蓬勃发展的灰色市场给奢侈品牌雪上加霜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-booming-grey-markets-add-woes-luxury-brands-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国的奢侈品二手市场和灰色市场正在蓬勃发展，在经济疲软的情况下，奢侈品牌的价格上涨促使一些消费者寻找更便宜的购买方式，加深了人们对路威酩轩集团(LVMH)等公司的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-booming-grey-markets-add-woes-luxury-brands-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨表示，德国汽车制造商不应害怕中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-carmakers-should-not-be-afraid-chinese-competition-says-scholz-2024-10-21/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周一在梅赛德斯-奔驰首家电池回收工厂开业时表示，德国汽车制造商不应害怕来自中国的竞争，他称这项投资是德国新工业政策议程的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-carmakers-should-not-be-afraid-chinese-competition-says-scholz-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克将在业绩公布日接受有关特斯拉机器人出租车押注的质询</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-face-questions-teslas-robotaxi-bets-results-day-2024-10-21/</link><description>特斯拉的投资者和分析师将有机会在周三就其自动驾驶出租车计划向首席执行官埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）进行拷问，届时这家电动汽车制造商将公布季度业绩。此前，本月特斯拉发布的季度业绩大肆宣传，但缺乏关键细节，导致股价遭受重挫。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 10:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-face-questions-teslas-robotaxi-bets-results-day-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度考虑通过俄罗斯进口蒙古焦煤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-imports-mongolian-coking-coal-via-russia-source-says-2024-10-21/</link><description>一位直接了解此事的高级政府官员表示，印度正在探索通过俄罗斯定期进口蒙古焦煤的方法，因为新德里试图避免过度依赖通过中国过境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-imports-mongolian-coking-coal-via-russia-source-says-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>高级官员称，印度和中国达成边境巡逻协议，可能缓解关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-have-arrived-border-patrolling-pact-indias-top-diplomat-says-2024-10-21/</link><description>印度外交大臣维克拉姆·米斯里周一表示，印度和中国已就在有争议的喜马拉雅边境巡逻达成协议，以解决四年来的军事对峙，为政治和商业关系正常化铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-have-arrived-border-patrolling-pact-indias-top-diplomat-says-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中信股份将以4.303亿美元出售麦当劳中国及香港业务股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/citic-sell-stake-mcdonalds-china-hong-kong-business-4303-mln-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国国有企业中信股份已同意以 4.303 亿美元的价格出售其在中国大陆和香港经营快餐连锁店麦当劳的公司 19.23% 的股份，全面退出该业务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/citic-sell-stake-mcdonalds-china-hong-kong-business-4303-mln-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>国家开发银行原副行长因受贿被判有期徒刑12年并处罚金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-development-bank-former-vp-given-12-years-jail-fine-bribery-2024-10-21/</link><description>据中央电视台周一报道，国家开发银行（CDB）前副行长王永胜因受贿罪被判处 12 年有期徒刑，并处罚金 200 万元人民币（28 万美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-development-bank-former-vp-given-12-years-jail-fine-bribery-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责缅甸总领事馆遇袭事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</link><description>中国外交部发言人表示，中国谴责周一针对中国驻曼德勒领事馆的袭击，并敦促缅甸当局尽一切努力逮捕肇事者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-attack-myanmar-consulate-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾任命总统顾问为APEC峰会代表</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</link><description>台湾总统府周一表示，已任命赖清德总统的一名高级顾问作为今年秘鲁亚太经合组织峰会的特使，这是台湾和中国大陆共同参加的少数国际论坛之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-appoints-presidential-advisor-apec-summit-representative-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia 获得为比亚迪位于土耳其的第二家欧洲工厂供货的协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-secures-deal-supply-byds-second-european-factory-turkey-2024-10-21/</link><description>按收入计算，全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周一表示，比亚迪已选择该公司为其位于土耳其的第二家欧洲工厂供货。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:29:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-secures-deal-supply-byds-second-european-factory-turkey-2024-10-21/</guid></item><item><title>联合国 COP16 谈判中世界在 2030 年自然目标方面落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</link><description>近 200 个国家齐聚哥伦比亚卡利，参加为期两周的联合国生物多样性峰会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 06:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/world-lags-2030-nature-goals-headed-into-un-cop16-talks-2024-10-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>